snippet.title: The Foretold: Westmark Legacy - Official Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description:
The Foretold: Westmark Legacy is a 2D gothic horror adventure card game developed by Nodbrim Interactive. Players will equip items and relics, attain powerful cards, and wield them wisely in order to survive what lies in the dark. The Foretold: Westmark Legacy is launching soon for PC with a demo available now on Steam.

#TheForetoldWestmarkLegacy #RealmsDeep2023
